flowchart TB

Auth[Tai khoan]

Auth --> Login[Dang nhap /Account/Login]
Auth --> Register[Chon loai dang ky /Account/Register]
Auth --> ForgotPassword[Quen mat khau /Account/ForgotPassword]
Auth --> Logout[Dang xuat /Account/Logout]

Register --> RegisterCandidate[Dang ky ung vien /Account/RegisterCandidate]
Register --> RegisterEmployer[Dang ky nha tuyen dung /Account/RegisterEmployer]

RegisterCandidate --> VerifyEmail[Xac thuc email /Account/VerifyEmail]
RegisterEmployer --> VerifyEmail

ForgotPassword --> ResetPassword[Dat lai mat khau /Account/ResetPassword]
ResetPassword --> VerifyEmail

Login --> CandidateHome[Khu vuc ung vien]
Login --> EmployerHome[Khu vuc nha tuyen dung]
Login --> AdminHome[Khu vuc quan tri]
